fields.instructions: Paste your Google Analytics (or other) tracking code here. This will be added into the head template of your theme. Please place code inside script tags.

fields.label: Custom CSS
fields.name: custom_css
fields.instructions: Paste your CSS code, do not include any tags or HTML in the field. Any custom CSS entered here will override the theme CSS. In some cases, the !important tag may be needed. Don't URL encode image or svg paths. Contents of this field will be auto encoded.
